The art of doing nothing is easy in Bellevue 🍃. With gorgeous parks and clean walkable streets, it makes the ideal place to escape the grind and unwind on your next bleisure or staycation trip.⁣
⁣
Join Mr. Little for a relaxing day as he embraces the stillness of 💧 float therapy @floatseattle. Then take in the simplistic natural beauty as he strolls through 📍 Bellevue Downtown Park & Meydenbauer Bay Park accompanied a delicious treat 🍦 from @mollymoonicecream. Why? Because it's nice to do nice things. So sit back and enjoy the Vue.

Come see the masterpiece from a whole new perspective 🤩⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
Michelangelo’s Sistine Chapel: The Exhibition 📍The Shops at the Bravern opens⁣ 📆 September 2, 2022, through October.⁣
⁣
Don't miss this awesome exhibit!⁣⁣ Head over to https://bit.ly/3q7b1lH for tickets.⁣ 🎥 video credit @chapelsistine

The perfect day does exist- stunning panoramic views, fun with friends, delicious food, and a sunset bagpipe serenade ⛳⁣⁣

⁣⁣Join Mr. Little for a fantastic day on the green at 📍The Golf Club at Newcastle. Only on the Vue! 🔗 link in bio to more episodes.

Join us on this 
dreamlike adventure as we glide through the air on a hot air balloon tour. 🎈🏔🥂⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Kara checks off an adventure on her bucket list with📍Seattle Ballooning ⏱ just 30 min from Bellevue. We hope you enjoy floating through this tranquil experience, only in the Vue! 🔗 to more episodes in the bio. 📸 cover photo @seattleballooning

Sushi FOMO is real. Fret not though, Friend- We got you covered.🍣⁣⁣

Bellevue has an incredible Sushi scene with fresh fish flown in from Japan and experienced Japanese sushi chefs to create the authentic sushi experience you've always wanted.⁣⁣

It's time to step out of your comfort zone and into Bellevue's thriving international culinary scene! 🌍⁣⁣

Join acclaimed chefs on a culinary journey!

This August, Bellevue becomes the stage for The Radiant Table. This is an extraordinary dining experience where chef-crafted dishes meet projection-mapped storytelling. 🌊🌲✨

Each night, a new acclaimed chef takes you on a culinary journey through the flavors of the Pacific Northwest. Kick off the evening with a signature cocktail, mingle in a beautiful lounge, then settle in for an intimate, multi-course feast where the visuals are as delicious as the food itself. @the.radiant.table

👨‍🍳 Meet the Chefs:
🗓️ Aug 8 – Brandon Muehl (Ascend Prime Steak & Sushi)
🗓️ Aug 14 – Aaron Tekulve (Surrell)
🗓️ Aug 21 – Dan Koommoo (Crafted Yakima)
🗓️ Aug 22 – Jason Wilson & Daniel Strutton (The Lakehouse)
🗓️ Aug 23 – Matthew Lewis (Where Ya At Matt)
🗓️ Aug 29 – Bobby Moore (Bis on Main)

Whether you’re a local foodie or visiting for an unforgettable night out, Radiant Table is your chance to taste, see, and feel the Pacific Northwest in a whole new way.

📅 August 8–31
📍 The Bellevue Collection

latestPosts.caption:
The latest episode of The Vue is serving up bold plant-based Vietnamese food 🍜🌿 

Our culinary ambassador @nelson_yong explores Chay Concept, a vegetarian Vietnamese gem in the heart of Bellevue that’s redefining tradition with every bite. Founded by Chef Van Nguyen and inspired by family recipes, Chay blends fragrant herbs, fresh ingredients, and creative twists (like imitation meats) to bring classic Vietnamese dishes to life — all with a plant-based spin.

🍽️ Must-try:
 – Pho Rolls (a Visit Bellevue staff favorite!)
 – Steamed Lotus Purple Rice
 – Vegetarian Pho & Banh Mi with a savory, satisfying twist

🔥 Don’t miss their weekly specials:
 🌱 Monday: 2 small plates for $20
 🍹 Tuesday: Buy 2, get 1 free drink
 ...and more all week long!

Whether you're vegan, vegetarian, or just curious about fresh takes on Vietnamese classics, Chay Concept is a flavorful experience you won’t want to miss.

Watch more by following the link in bio!

Molly Tea is opening in Bellevue, WA! ☕️🧸🧋

Molly Tea, originally from Shenzhen, China, is opening their FIRST Washington shop in Downtown Bellevue! ✨ They’re known for their jasmine milk tea drinks and light, fragrant floral teas. 🤗🌼

Featured Drinks:
🍵 Premium Jasmine Matcha + Cheese Matcha Foam
🧋 Peach Oolong Milk Tea

Soft Opening on Friday, June 27th at 11:00 AM! 🎉

Molly Tea 
📍103 Bellevue Way NE, Bellevue, WA 98004

⭐️ SOFT OPENING PROMOS ⭐️
• 12% off ALL in-store purchases from June 27 - July 3! 
• BUY 1, GET 1 FREE July 4 -July 6!

Thank you @mollytea_bellevue and @seattle_fantuan_delivery for inviting me 🫶🏼

Celebrate 4th of July in Bellevue! 🎆

The Eastside’s biggest Independence Day celebration is back and better than ever! Whether you're soaking up the sun on Lake Washington, cheering on the Mariners, or enjoying a rooftop fireworks view with a craft cocktail in hand—Bellevue has everything you need for an unforgettable 4th of July weekend.

Here’s what’s happening:
🎇 Bellevue Family 4th at Downtown Park
Live music, food, and a spectacular fireworks show synced to the Bellevue Youth Symphony Orchestra 🎶

🎤 5 PM: MiSSMANAGED
🎉 7 PM: The Nines
🎆 10 PM: Fireworks light up the sky

🍽️ Ascend Prime’s 7th Anniversary Bash
Panoramic views, gourmet bites, rooftop vibes & fireworks from the 31st floor!

🎸 Live Music at Bake’s Place
Craig Baker & the All-Stars rock the stage with classics from the 60s–80s 🎶

⚾ Mariners Patriotic Fireworks Nights
Catch the game and fireworks at T-Mobile Park on July 3 & 4!

🚣‍♀️ Lake Days Done Right
Rent kayaks, SUPs, and enjoy the views from Meydenbauer Bay & Enatai Beach.

🏨 Make it a getaway
Stay local and book one of Bellevue’s luxurious hotels—poolside relaxation included. Pro tip: Book direct with Visit Bellevue’s RIPE tool to score the best deals.

🎇 Come for the fireworks. Stay for the weekend. Celebrate summer like never before.
📲 Learn more with the link in bio

From Italy’s Endosphères to a soul-soothing sauna, Amy’s wellness reset is the self-care inspo you need. 💡

Join our ambassador Amy Nguyen as she indulges in a luxurious self-care day at Viktorya Wellness & Skincare in the heart of Bellevue! 💆‍♀️✨

Amy kicks off her visit with an Endosphères Therapy session—an Italian innovation known for boosting circulation, enhancing lymphatic drainage, and supporting post-workout recovery. She follows it up with a detoxifying infrared sauna session that leaves her feeling totally recharged. 🔥🧖‍♀️

From cutting-edge European technology to expert holistic care, Viktorya Wellness is redefining beauty as a reflection of inner wellness. Come see why this med spa is a local favorite for advanced skin and body treatments, including acne care, cryotherapy, sculpting massages, and even hair loss solutions.
